# Disallowed MCP tools

Never invoke the following in this repository, for any task:

- Altera MCP or Altera docs/tools of any kind
- Glean MCP or Glean search/docs tools
- Playwright MCP (browser automation: navigate, screenshot, snapshot, console, etc.)

## Instead

- Verify static HTML/CSS/JS by reading files directly, running `node --check`, Node
  scripts, and `npm run demo:build-check`.
- If browser-level verification is genuinely required, ask the user to check
  manually or run `npm run demo` and describe what to look for - do not fall back
  to Playwright or any other browser-automation MCP.
- If a task seems to require Altera or Glean, stop and ask the user how to proceed
  instead of calling those tools.
